headline: NTLA Stock Up More Than 6% as FDA Lifts ATTRv-PN Study Clinical Hold
summary: Intellia jumps over 6% after the FDA lifts the clinical hold on the MAGNITUDE-2 study, clearing a path to resume dosing of nex-z in ATTRv-PN.
